<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>HMPI Water Quality Report</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica', 'Arial', sans-serif;
            font-size: 11pt;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background: white;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 210mm;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20mm;
        }

        /* Header Styles */
        .report-header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            padding-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #2563eb;
        }

        .report-title {
            font-size: 24pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #1e40af;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .report-subtitle {
            font-size: 14pt;
            color: #64748b;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .report-meta {
            font-size: 10pt;
            color: #94a3b8;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        /* Section Styles */
        .section {
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            page-break-inside: avoid;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-size: 16pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #1e40af;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
        }

        .section-subtitle {
            font-size: 12pt;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #475569;
            margin-top: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        /* Summary Cards */
        .summary-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
            gap: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .summary-card {
            background: #f8fafc;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .summary-card-title {
            font-size: 10pt;
            color: #64748b;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
        }

        .summary-card-value {
            font-size: 20pt;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #1e40af;
        }

        .summary-card-label {
            font-size: 9pt;
            color: #94a3b8;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }

        /* Statistics Table */
        .stats-table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .stats-table th,
        .stats-table td {
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: left;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }

        .stats-table th {
            background: #f1f5f9;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #475569;
            font-size: 10pt;
        }

        .stats-table td {
            font-size: 10pt;
        }

        .stats-table tr:hover {
            background: #f8fafc;
        }

        /* Chart Container */
        .chart-container {
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
            page-break-inside: avoid;
        }

        .chart-title {
            font-size: 11pt;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #475569;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .chart-image {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        /* Top Polluters List */
        .polluter-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .polluter-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            background: #f8fafc;
            border-left: 4px solid #ef4444;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .polluter-rank {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #64748b;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        .polluter-station {
            flex: 1;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1e40af;
        }

        .polluter-value {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #ef4444;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        .polluter-location {
            font-size: 9pt;
            color: #64748b;
        }

        /* Geographic Distribution */
        .geo-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 10px;
        }

        .geo-item {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            padding: 8px 12px;
            background: #f8fafc;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 10pt;
        }

        .geo-name {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #475569;
        }

        .geo-count {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #2563eb;
        }

        /* Recommendations */
        .recommendation-box {
            background: #fef3c7;
            border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 15px 0;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .recommendation-box h4 {
            color: #92400e;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-size: 11pt;
        }

        .recommendation-box ul {
            margin-left: 20px;
            color: #78350f;
        }

        .recommendation-box li {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            font-size: 10pt;
        }

        /* Footer */
        .report-footer {
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 2px solid #e2e8f0;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 9pt;
            color: #94a3b8;
        }

        /* Page Break */
        .page-break {
            page-break-after: always;
        }

        /* Print Styles */
        @media print {
            body {
                print-color-adjust: exact;
                -webkit-print-color-adjust: exact;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <!-- Report Header -->
        <div class="report-header">
            <h1 class="report-title">HMPI Water Quality Analysis Report</h1>
            <div class="report-subtitle">Comprehensive Assessment of Water Quality Indices</div>
            <div class="report-meta">
                <div>Report Generated: {{generatedDate}}</div>
                <div>Data File: {{uploadFilename}}</div>
                <div>Total Stations Analyzed: {{totalStations}}</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Executive Summary -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">Executive Summary</h2>
            
            <div class="summary-grid">
                <div class="summary-card">
                    <div class="summary-card-title">Average HPI</div>
                    <div class="summary-card-value">{{avgHPI}}</div>
                    <div class="summary-card-label">Heavy Metal Pollution Index</div>
                </div>
                <div class="summary-card">
                    <div class="summary-card-title">Average MI</div>
                    <div class="summary-card-value">{{avgMI}}</div>
                    <div class="summary-card-label">Metal Index</div>
                </div>
                <div class="summary-card">
                    <div class="summary-card-title">Average WQI</div>
                    <div class="summary-card-value">{{avgWQI}}</div>
                    <div class="summary-card-label">Water Quality Index</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <p style="margin-top: 20px; text-align: justify;">
                This report presents a comprehensive analysis of water quality across {{totalStations}} monitoring stations. 
                The assessment includes Heavy Metal Pollution Index (HPI), Metal Index (MI), and Water Quality Index (WQI) 
                measurements to evaluate the overall water quality and identify areas of concern.
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- HPI Analysis -->
        <div class="section page-break">
            <h2 class="section-title">Heavy Metal Pollution Index (HPI) Analysis</h2>
            
            <h3 class="section-subtitle">Classification Distribution</h3>
            <table class="stats-table">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Classification</th>
                        <th style="text-align: right;">Number of Stations</th>
                        <th style="text-align: right;">Percentage</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {{#each hpiClassifications}}
                    <tr>
                        <td>{{classification}}</td>
                        <td style="text-align: right;">{{count}}</td>
                        <td style="text-align: right;">{{percentage}}%</td>
                    </tr>
                    {{/each}}
                </tbody>
            </table>

            <div class="chart-container">
                <div class="chart-title">HPI Classification Distribution</div>
                <img src="data:image/png;base64,{{hpiDistributionChart}}" class="chart-image" alt="HPI Distribution">
            </div>

            <div class="chart-container">
                <div class="chart-title">HPI Classification Breakdown</div>
                <img src="data:image/png;base64,{{hpiClassificationChart}}" class="chart-image" alt="HPI Classification">
            </div>

            <h3 class="section-subtitle">Top 10 Most Polluted Stations</h3>
            <ul class="polluter-list">
                {{#each topPollutedStations}}
                <li class="polluter-item">
                    <span class="polluter-rank">{{rank}}.</span>
                    <span class="polluter-station">{{stationId}}</span>
                    <span class="polluter-value">HPI: {{hpi}}</span>
                    {{#if location}}
                    <span class="polluter-location">{{location}}</span>
                    {{/if}}
                </li>
                {{/each}}
            </ul>

            <div class="chart-container">
                <div class="chart-title">Top Polluted Stations by HPI</div>
                <img src="data:image/png;base64,{{topPollutedChart}}" class="chart-image" alt="Top Polluted Stations">
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- MI Analysis -->
        <div class="section page-break">
            <h2 class="section-title">Metal Index (MI) Analysis</h2>
            
            <h3 class="section-subtitle">Classification Distribution</h3>
            <table class="stats-table">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Classification</th>
                        <th style="text-align: right;">Number of Stations</th>
                        <th style="text-align: right;">Percentage</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {{#each miClassifications}}
                    <tr>
                        <td>{{classification}}</td>
                        <td style="text-align: right;">{{count}}</td>
                        <td style="text-align: right;">{{percentage}}%</td>
                    </tr>
                    {{/each}}
                </tbody>
            </table>

            <div class="chart-container">
                <div class="chart-title">MI Classification Distribution</div>
                <img src="data:image/png;base64,{{miDistributionChart}}" class="chart-image" alt="MI Distribution">
            </div>

            <div class="chart-container">
                <div class="chart-title">MI Classification Breakdown</div>
                <img src="data:image/png;base64,{{miClassificationChart}}" class="chart-image" alt="MI Classification">
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- WQI Analysis -->
        <div class="section page-break">
            <h2 class="section-title">Water Quality Index (WQI) Analysis</h2>
            
            <h3 class="section-subtitle">Classification Distribution</h3>
            <table class="stats-table">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Classification</th>
                        <th style="text-align: right;">Number of Stations</th>
                        <th style="text-align: right;">Percentage</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    {{#each wqiClassifications}}
                    <tr>
                        <td>{{classification}}</td>
                        <td style="text-align: right;">{{count}}</td>
                        <td style="text-align: right;">{{percentage}}%</td>
                    </tr>
                    {{/each}}
                </tbody>
            </table>

            <div class="chart-container">
                <div class="chart-title">WQI Classification Distribution</div>
                <img src="data:image/png;base64,{{wqiDistributionChart}}" class="chart-image" alt="WQI Distribution">
            </div>

            <div class="chart-container">
                <div class="chart-title">WQI Classification Breakdown</div>
                <img src="data:image/png;base64,{{wqiClassificationChart}}" class="chart-image" alt="WQI Classification">
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Geographic Distribution -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">Geographic Distribution</h2>
            
            <h3 class="section-subtitle">Stations by State</h3>
            <div class="geo-grid">
                {{#each geoStates}}
                <div class="geo-item">
                    <span class="geo-name">{{state}}</span>
                    <span class="geo-count">{{count}} stations</span>
                </div>
                {{/each}}
            </div>

            <div class="chart-container">
                <div class="chart-title">Geographic Distribution (Top States)</div>
                <img src="data:image/png;base64,{{geographicChart}}" class="chart-image" alt="Geographic Distribution">
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Recommendations -->
        <div class="section">
            <h2 class="section-title">Recommendations</h2>
            
            {{#if hasHighPollution}}
            <div class="recommendation-box">
                <h4>‚ö†Ô∏è High Pollution Areas Detected</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Immediate water quality intervention required for critically polluted stations</li>
                    <li>Conduct detailed source identification studies for high HPI locations</li>
                    <li>Implement regular monitoring programs with increased sampling frequency</li>
                    <li>Consider water treatment solutions for affected areas</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            {{/if}}

            <div class="recommendation-box">
                <h4>üìã General Recommendations</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Continue routine monitoring of all stations to track trends</li>
                    <li>Establish baseline values for each monitoring location</li>
                    <li>Implement source control measures in areas showing degradation</li>
                    <li>Develop watershed management plans for affected regions</li>
                    <li>Engage stakeholders in water quality improvement initiatives</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="report-footer">
            <p>This report was automatically generated by the Nirmaya HMPI System</p>
            <p>For technical queries, please contact the system administrator</p>
            <p>&copy; {{year}} Nirmaya Water Quality Monitoring System</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
